{"tid":468132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉藏K仔被控  40歲休班男警否認藏毒罪","createTime":"2017-11-14T06:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T08:49:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6e0037aea3999e6341e013fac4980ff9b7594230","tid":468132,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:15:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171114/57456292\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171114%2F57456292&d=UPjA6PuRRITyKL%2B8B9ZvRDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=a6bc5065\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171114%2F57456292&h=3287c219\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171114/57456292</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171114/large/1510630643_5bf2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171114%2Flarge%2F1510630643_5bf2.jpg&h=6d5422a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n休班男警在街上遇到同袍截查時，被發現身上涉藏有少量俗稱K仔的毒品氯氨酮。警員被控藏毒罪，他今在裁判法院否認控罪，續准保釋至下月27日案件開審。<br />\n<br />\n被告潘俊東（40歲）被控於去年10月28日在荃灣綠楊新邨D座旁的行人路管有危險藥物，即0.38克氯胺酮。控方將有4名證人，而辯方將由外籍私人大律師代表出庭。"},{"pid":"a85bfaf7a05f09a4c41e471f4e72cd66e68eeeed","tid":468132,"uid":60074,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:16:42.000Z","msg":"休班警+1分"},{"pid":"b86a1b82e6d0646bb6e860435cc39aa54d4a5375","tid":468132,"uid":66784,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:23:57.000Z","msg":"可能本來諗住塞落mk仔褲袋"},{"pid":"66a1945c83a6d3da295634f7161a96eaa60826f3","tid":468132,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:30:03.000Z","msg":"個頭Mk到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9ca710833da22370ac66540f3bc072ec1f0dbc","tid":468132,